metadata.name: The Moodguys #828
metadata.description: Each unique symbolic avatar from the MoodGuys collection symbolizes the power, energy that is given to each person by nature. Listen to your inner voice, not to the voice of centralized systems. Life is very short. The winners are those who understand this from the very beginning. We, the owners of MoodGuys tokens, write and draw our history. The history of the decentralized universe.
